  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "An ***error message*** is a piece of writing that tells a user something went wrong and, ideally, what to do about it. Error messages are among the most frequently read and least carefully written texts in software — and among the most consequential, because they appear at the exact moment the user is frustrated and needs help.",
